text: Wide range of shampoo for your fur kids needs and gentle on skin! Affordable and cute packaging as well
Lots of favour shampoos for fur kids, the fragrance is good to smell after showering and gentle on the doggies.
Shampoo smells really good, love the packaging as well

What stood out the most was the pleasant, subtle scent—it’s not overpowering but leaves your dog smelling fresh for days. I also appreciate that it’s made with natural ingredients and is free from harsh chemicals.
I got 2 dogs and require to try out on each of them on different shampoo
